{"title":"两地书","authors":["程光锐"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"两地书\t程光锐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄华东天高云淡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬望眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍找南飞雁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捎封信儿到华东，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交给那英雄汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先祝胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里的话再细谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闻捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我多喜欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨飞贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怒火冲九天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海盗大猖狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我领空犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你，英雄汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为祖国立了功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭了敌人的凶焰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请接受我的敬礼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺便问，事一件："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打落黑乌鸦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可曾捉住那罪犯？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请回信，谈一谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万，千万！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还请捎来点战利品，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"譬如飞机小碎片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好留作纪念！\t  寄北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托南风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回信北京传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢谢同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问候和思念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情长纸短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间有限，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天要开祝捷会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚要值班，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能稍写几句话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谈一谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你提的问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回答也不难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正发言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯尼迪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他就是罪犯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁证如山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看他今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民面前站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭也哭不得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辩又如何辩？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"羞惭惭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹抱橄榄枝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半遮面……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}